Package: mixtime
Type: Package
Title: Mixing Time Statistics
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ali Taqi
Maintainer: Ali Taqi <alif.taqi00@gmail.com>
Description: Simulate stochastic matrices and analyze mixing time statistics.
    The package allows the user to either simulate stochastic matrices or provide one. Given a matrix
    the user can generate a large batch of initial probability distributions and analyzing the mixing time
    statistics.
License: Common license
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
